{
  "texts": [
    "For copper ore, Turkey, Spain, and Brazil are consistently the top three most likely causes for concern.",
    "For unrefined copper, Chile, Bulgaria, Sweden, and Germany appear most often as the likely causes for concern.",
    "For refined copper, the United States, Germany, and Chile appear most frequently.",
    "On the other hand, other countries only appear in more specific scenarios.",
    "For example, Zambia does not appear until the 20% loss level for unrefined copper and Belgium only appears in refined copper at the 5% loss level."
  ]
}